<inglise> - prepare and chair meetings of the Council of the EMI; </inglise>
<eesti> - valmistab ette ja juhatab ERI n&otilde;ukogu istungeid; </eesti>
<inglise> - without prejudice to Article 22, present the views of the EMI externally; </inglise>
