<inglise> Interinstitutional cooperation and reporting requirements </inglise>
<eesti> Institutsioonidevaheline koost&ouml;&ouml; ja aruandekohustus </eesti>
<inglise> 11.1 The President of the Council and a member of the Commission may participate, without having the right to vote, in meetings of the Council of the EMI. </inglise>
<eesti> 11.1. ERI n&otilde;ukogu istungitest v&otilde;ivad h&auml;&auml;le&otilde;iguseta osa v&otilde;tta n&otilde;ukogu president ja &uuml;ks komisjoni liige. </eesti>
<inglise> 11.2. </inglise>
<eesti> 11.2. </eesti>
<inglise> The President of the EMI shall be invited to participate in Council meetings when the Council is discussing matters relating to the objectives and tasks of the EMI. </inglise>
<eesti> ERI president kutsutakse osa v&otilde;tma n&otilde;ukogu istungitest, kui n&otilde;ukogu arutab ERI eesm&auml;rkide ja &uuml;lesannetega seotud k&uuml;simusi. </eesti>
<inglise> 11.3. </inglise>
<eesti> 11.3. </eesti>
<inglise> At a date to be established in the Rules of Procedure, the EMI shall prepare an annual report on its activities and on monetary and financial conditions in the Community. </inglise>
<eesti> Kodukorraga etten&auml;htud ajal esitab ERI majandusaasta aruande oma tegevuse ning valuuta- ja finantsolukorra kohta &uuml;henduses. </eesti>
<inglise> The annual report, together with the annual accounts of the EMI, shall be addressed to the European Parliament, the Council and the Commission and also to the European Council. </inglise>
<eesti> Majandusaasta aruanne koos ERI raamatupidamise aastaaruandega saadetakse Euroopa Parlamendile, n&otilde;ukogule ja komisjonile ning samuti Euroopa &Uuml;lemkogule. </eesti>
<inglise> The President of the EMI may, at the request of the European Parliament or on his own initiative, be heard by the competent Committees of the European Parliament. </inglise>
<eesti> Euroopa Parlamendi taotlusel v&otilde;i omal algatusel v&otilde;ib ERI president esineda Euroopa Parlamendi p&auml;devate komiteede ees. </eesti>
<inglise> 11.4. </inglise>
<eesti> 11.4. </eesti>
<inglise> Reports published by the EMI shall be made available to interested parties free of charge. </inglise>
<eesti> ERI avaldatud aruanded tehakse huvitatud pooltele k&auml;ttesaadavaks tasuta. </eesti>
<inglise> ARTICLE 12 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 12 </eesti>
<inglise> Currency denomination </inglise>
