<inglise> Judicial control and related matters. </inglise>
<eesti> Kohtulik kontroll ja sellega seotud k&uuml;simused </eesti>
<inglise> 19.1. </inglise>
<eesti> 19.1. </eesti>
<inglise> The acts or omissions of the EMI shall be open to review or interpretation by the Court of Justice in the cases and under the conditions laid down in this Treaty. </inglise>
